Rating: 4
Very simple and quick to make. The flavors blend to create a very unique taste. Everyone in my family, from the youngest (2) to the oldest (42) liked it quite a bit. The only possible change would be a touch more salt. We will definitely make this again!

Rating: 4
My boyfriend thought I was crazy when I put the corn straight on the grill rather than wrapping it in foil first, but he ate his words! I used cilantro instead of thyme in the butter because I am a cilantro addict, and it turned out AMAZING! I used the extra butter on white rice and to butter bread. Delish!

